field_mount_path_placeholder.message: indlela ezenzakalelayo uhla lwemibhalo lwasekhaya lomsebenzisi

hterm_name_pref_alt_is_meta.message: Phatha ukhiye othi Alt njengokhiye we-Meta

hterm_name_pref_desktop_notification_bel.message: Dala izaziso zedeskithophu ukuthola izikhalisi zesixwayiso

hterm_name_pref_east_asian_ambiguous_as_.message: I-East Asian Ambiguous isebenzisa amakholomu amabili

hterm_name_pref_enable_8_bit_control.message: Sekela izinhlamvu zokulawula ezingeyona i-UTF-8 C1

hterm_name_pref_enable_clipboard_write.message: Vumela ukubhala ebhodini lokunamathisela lokulawula kude

hterm_name_pref_enable_resize_status.message: Bonisa ubukhulu betheminali lapho kushintshwe usayizi

hterm_name_pref_page_keys_scroll.message: Ukuziphatha kokuskrola kokhiye wokuthi Khuphuka/Yehla Ekhasini

hterm_pref_allow_images_inline.message:
Ukuthi uvumele yini umsingathi wokulawula-kude ukubonisa izithombe kutheminali.

Ngokuzenzakalelayo, sixwayisa kuze kube yilapho kwenziwe isinqumo.

hterm_pref_alt_backspace_is_meta_backspa.message: Uma kusethiwe, kuhlehlisa i-Chrome OS Alt+Backspace->Delete kokumepha kabusha, ukuze u-Alt+Backspace abe ngu-Alt+Backspace.

hterm_pref_alt_gr_mode.message:
Khetha ukuthola i-AltGr heuristic.

'null': Thola ngokuzenzekelayo ngokususelwe ku-navigator.language:
      'en-us' => 'none', else => 'right-alt'
'none': Khubaza noma yikuphi ukulingisa i-AltGr.
'ctrl-alt': U-Ctrl+Alt usho u-AltGr.
'left-alt': Iya ngakwesokunxele u-Alt usho AltGr.
'right-alt': Iya ngakwesokudla u-Alt usho AltGr.

hterm_pref_alt_is_meta.message: Ukuthi ukhiye we-Alt usebenza njengokhiye we-Meta noma njengokhiye we-Alt ohlukile.

hterm_pref_alt_sends_what.message:
Kulawula indlela ukhiye othi Alt ophathwa ngayo.

  escape: Thumela isiqalo se-ESC.
  8-bit: Engeza u-128 kuhlamvu oluthayiphiwe njenge-xterm.
 browser-key: Linda umcimbi wokucindezela ukhiye bese ubona lokho okushiwo
 isiphequluli. (Lokhu ngeke kusebenze kuzo zonke izinkundla lapho isiphequluli
 sisebenza khona njengesenzo esizenzakalelayo kokunye ukulandelana kwe-Alt.)

hterm_pref_audible_bell_sound.message: I-URL yomsindo wesikhalisi setheminali. Kushiye kungenalutho kwisikhalisi esizwakalayo.

hterm_pref_background_color.message: Umbala wangemuva wombhalo ongenazo ezinye izibaluli zombala.

hterm_pref_background_image.message:
Inani le-CSS lomfanekiso ongemuva Kuyeke kungenaso isithombe.

Ngokwesibonelo:
  url(https://goo.gl/anedTK)
  linear-gradient(top bottom, blue, red)

hterm_pref_background_position.message:
Inani le-CSS lokuma komfanekiso wangemuva.

Ngokwesibonelo:
  10% 10%
  center

hterm_pref_backspace_sends_backspace.message: Uma kuyiqiniso, okhiye othi Backspace uzothumela i-BS ('\x08', aka ^H). Noma ukhiye othi Backspace uzothumela i-'\x7f'.

hterm_pref_clear_selection_after_copy.message: Ukuthi usule yini okukhethiwe ngemva kokukopisha.

hterm_pref_close_on_exit.message: Ukuthi ulivale yini iwindi lapho umyalo uqeda ukusayinda.

hterm_pref_color_palette_overrides.message:
Khipha imibala kwisiceshana sokuxuba imibala esizenzakalelayo.

Lokhu kungacaciswa njengohlu noma into. Uma kucacishwe njengento kungase kube uhlu oluncane, lapho isakhiwo ngasinye siyinkomba yezinombolo kwisiceshana sokuxuba imibala.

Amanani angacaciswa cishe njenganoma yiliphi inani lombala we-CSS. Lokhu kuhlanganisa okuthi #RGB, #RRGGBB, rgb(...), rgba(...), nanoma yimaphi amagama ombala ayingxenye yefayela le-X11 rgb.txt elivamile.

Ungasebenzisa okuthi 'null' ukucacisa ukuthi inani elizenzakalelayo akufanele lishintshwe. Lokhu kuwusizo ukweqa inani eliphansi lezinkomba lapho inani licaciswe njengohlu.

Ngokwesibonelo, lokhu kokubili kusetha inkomba yombala ewu-1 ibe luhlaza okwesibhakabhaka:
  {1: "#0000ff"}
  [null, "#0000ff"]

hterm_pref_copy_on_select.message: Kopisha ngokuzenzekelayo okukhethiwe kwegundane ebhodi lokunamathisela.

hterm_pref_ctrl_c_copy.message:
U-Ctrl+C uyakopisha uma kuyiqiniso, thumela okuthi ^C kumsingathi uma kungamanga.
U-Ctrl+Shift+C uthumela okuthi ^C kumsingathi uma kuyiqiniso, kuyakopisha uma kungamanga.

hterm_pref_ctrl_plus_minus_zero_zoom.message:
Uma kuyiqiniso, u-Ctrl+Plus/Minus/Zero kulawula ukusondeza.
Uma kungamanga, u-Ctrl+Shift+Plus/Minus/Zero kulawula ukusondeza, u-Ctrl+Minus uthumela i-^_, u-Ctrl+Plus/Zero awenzi lutho.

hterm_pref_ctrl_v_paste.message:
U-Ctrl+V uyanamathisela uma kuyiqiniso, thumela u-^V kumsingathi uma kungamanga.
U-Ctrl+Shift+V sends ^V uthumela kumsingathi uma kuyiqiniso, uyanamathisela uma kungamanga.

hterm_pref_cursor_blink.message: Ukuthi i-cursor yombhalo ibanika ngokuzenzakalelayo yini. Lokhu kungaguqulwa ngesikhathi sokusebenzisa ngokulandelana kokuphuma ngetheminali.

hterm_pref_cursor_blink_cycle.message:
Isilinganisela sokubanika kwe-cursor yombhalo ngama-millisecond.

Uhla lwezici ezimbili, esokuqala ukuthi i-cursor kufanele ihlale ivuliwe isikhathi esingakanani, esesibili ukuthi kufanele ihlale ivaliwe isikhathi esingakanani.

hterm_pref_cursor_shape.message: Umumo we-cursor yombhalo obonakalayo. Lokhu kungashintsha ngesikhathi sokusebenza ngokulandelana kokuphuma ngetheminali.

hterm_pref_desktop_notification_bell.message:
Uma kuyiqiniso, izikhalisi zetheminali zangemuva zizodala Isaziso sewebhu. https://www.w3.org/TR/notifications/

Ukubonisa izaziso kudinga imvume kusuka kubasebenzisi. Lapho le nketho isethwe kokuthi iqiniso, i-hterm izozama ukucela umsebenzisi imvume uma kudingekile. Iziphequluli zingase zingasibonisi lesi sicelo semvume uma singazange sibangelwe isenzo somsebenzisi.

Izandiso ze-Chrome ezinemvume "yezaziso" zinemvume yokubonisa izaziso.

hterm_pref_east_asian_ambiguous_as_two_c.message: Ukuthi izinhlamvu ze-East Asian Ambiguous zinabo yini ububanzi bekholomu obubili.

hterm_pref_enable_8_bit_control.message:
Kuyiqiniso ukunika amandla izinhlamvu zokulawula kwe-8-bit, kungamanga ukukuziba.

Sizohlonipha izinguqulo zamabhayithi amabili walezi zinhlamvu zokulawula kungakhathaliseki isethingi yazo.

hterm_pref_enable_blink.message: Uma kuyiqiniso, hlonipha isibaluli sokubanika. Uma kungamanga, kuzibe.

hterm_pref_enable_bold.message: Uma kuyiqiniso, ifonti yesisindo esigqamile yombhalo onesibaluli esigqamile/esikhanyayo. Uma kungamanga, sebenzisa ifonti yesisindo esivamile. Kuyize ekutholeni ngokuzenzakalelayo.

hterm_pref_enable_bold_as_bright.message: Uma kuyiqiniso, imibala ekhanyayo (engu-8-15 kwisiceshana sokuxuba imibala esingu-16) kunoma yimuphi umbhalo onesibaluli esigqamile. Uma kungamanga.

hterm_pref_enable_clipboard_notice.message: Ukuthi ubonise yini umlayezo kutheminali lapho umsingathi ebhala ebhodini lokunamathisela.

hterm_pref_enable_clipboard_write.message:
Vumela umsingathi wokulawula kude ukubhala ngokuqondile ebhodini lokunamathisela lesistimu yendawo.
Ukufinyelela kokufunda akunikezwa ngaphandle kwale sethingi.

Lokhu kusetshenziselwa ukulawula ukufinyelela ezicini ezifana ne-OSC-52.

hterm_pref_enable_csi_j_3.message:
Ukuthi umsebenzi othi Sula Imigqa Elondoloziwe (imodi 3) yomyalo othi Sula Isiboniso (CSI-J) ungase usule ibhafa yokubuyela emuva yetheminal.

Ukunika amandla lokhu ngokuzenzakalela kuphephile.

hterm_pref_enable_dec12.message: Hlonipha umzamo kamsingathi wokushintsha isimo sokubanika kwe-cursor yombhalo usebenzisa i-DEC Private Mode 12.

hterm_pref_enable_resize_status.message: Ukuthi ukubonise yini ubukhulu betheminali lapho itheminali ishintsha usayizi.

hterm_pref_foreground_color.message: Umbala ophambili wombhalo ongenazo ezinye izibaluli zombala.

hterm_pref_hide_mouse_while_typing.message:
Ukuthi ufihle yini ngokuzenzekelayo i-cursor yombhalo lapho uthayipha. Ngokuzenzakalela, thola ngokuzenzakalelayo noma ngabe inkundla/OS ebamba lokhu.

Qaphela: Isistimu yakho yokusebenza ingase ikhiphe le sethingi futhi ungase ungakwazi ukuyikhubaza ngaso sonke isikhathi.

hterm_pref_home_keys_scroll.message: Uma kuyiqiniso, u-Home/End ulawula ibha yokuskrola yetheminali futhi u-Shift+Home/Shift+End uthunyelwa kumsingathi wokulawula kude. Uma kungamanga, u-Home/End uthunyelwa kumsingathi wokulawula kude futhi u-Shift+Home/Shift+End uyaskrola.

hterm_pref_keybindings.message:
Imephu yokulandelana kokhiye kwizenzo zokhiye. Ukulandelana kokhiye kufaka phakathi okhiye bokushintsha abayiqanda noma ngaphezulu kulandelwa ikhodi yokhiye. Amakhodi wokhiye angaba izinombolo ze-decimal noma ze-hexadecimal, noma inkomba yokhiye. Izenzo zokhiye zingacaciswa njengeyunithi yezinhlamvu yokuthumela kumsingathi, noma inkomba yesenzo. Ukuthola incazelo egcwele yefomethi, bona ku-https://goo.gl/LWRndr.

Isampula lokubhophezela okhiye:
{
  "Ctrl+Alt+K": "clearTerminal",
  "Ctrl+Shift+L": "PASS",
  "Ctrl+H": "'Sawubona Mhlaba'"
}

hterm_pref_keybindings_os_defaults.message: Ukuthi ukubophezela kwekhibhodi ye-OS kufanele kuhlonishwe yini esikhundleni sokuthathela ukusetshenziswa kwe-hterm ngokwayo.

hterm_pref_media_keys_are_fkeys.message: Uma kuyiqiniso, guqula okhiye bemidiya babe okulinganayo kwabo kwe-Fkey. Uma kungamanga, vumela isiphequluli sibambe okhiye.

hterm_pref_meta_sends_escape.message:
Thumela isiqalo se-ESC lapho ucindezela ukhiye ngenkathi ubambe ukhiye we-Meta.

Ngokwesibonelo, lapho kunikwe amandla, ukucindezela u-Meta+K kuzothumela okuthi ^[k sengathi uthayiphe u-Escape no-k. Lapho kukhutshaziwe, u-k kuphela ozothunyelwa.

hterm_pref_mouse_right_click_paste.message:
Namathisela ngokuchofoza ngakwesokudla kwinkinobho yegundane .

Le nketho ayisekelwe kwisethingi "yenkinobho yokunamathisela ngegundane".

Qaphela: Lokhu kuzobamba kahle igundane lesandla esingakwesokunxele nesingakwesokudla.

hterm_pref_page_keys_scroll.message: Uma kuyiqiniso, u-Page Up/Page Down ulawula ibha yokuskrola yetheminali futhi u-Shift+Page Up/Shift+Page Down uthunyelwa kumsingathi wokulawula kude. Uma kungamanga, u-Page Up/Page Down uthunyelwa kumsingathi wokulawula kude futhi u-Shift+Page Up/Shift+Page Down uyaskrola.

hterm_pref_pass_alt_number.message:
Ukuthi u-Alt+1..9 udluliselwe yini kwisiphequluli.

Lokhu kuwusizo lapho usebenzisa i-hterm kuthebhu yesiphequluli, ukuze ungalahlekelwa izinqamuleli zekhibhodi ze-Chrome zokuthi "shintshela kwithebhu". Lapho kungasebenzi kuthebhu kungcono ukuthumela labo khiye kumsingathi ukuze basetshenziswe ku-vim noma ku-emacs.

Uma kuyiqiniso, u-Alt+1..9 uzosingathwa isiphequluli. Uma kungamanga, u-Alt+1..9 uzothunyelwa kumsingathi. Uma kuyize, thola ngokuzenzekelayo ngokususelwe kwinkundla yesiphequluli nohlobo lewindi.

hterm_pref_pass_ctrl_n.message:
Ukuthi i-Ctrl+N iyadluliswa yini kwisiphequluli.

Uma kuyiqiniso, i-Ctrl+N izobanjwa isiphequluli njengesinqamuleli sekhibhodi "sewindi elisha". Uma kungamanga, i-Ctrl+N izothunyelwa kumsingathi.

hterm_pref_pass_ctrl_number.message:
Ukuthi u-Ctrl+1..9 uyadluliselwa yini kwisiphequluli.

Lokhu kuwusizo lapho usebenzisa i-hterm kuthebhu yesiphequluli, ukuze ungalahlekelwa izinqamuleli zekhibhodi ze-Chrome zokuthi "shintshela kwithebhu". Lapho kungasebenzi kuthebhu kungcono ukuthumela labo khiye kumsingathi ukuze basetshenziswe ku-vim noma ku-emacs.

Uma kuyiqiniso, u-Ctrl+1..9 uzobanjwa isiphequluli. Uma kungamanga, u-Ctrl+1..9 uzothunyelwa kumsingathi. Uma kuyize, thola ngokuzenzekelayo ngokususelwe kwinkundla yesiphequluli nohlobo lewindi.

hterm_pref_pass_ctrl_t.message:
Ukuthi u-Ctrl+T udlulisiwe yini kwisiphequluli

Uma kuyiqiniso, u-Ctrl+T uzophathwa isiphequluli njengesinqamuleli sekhibhodi "sethebhu entsha". Uma kungamanga, u-Ctrl+T uzothunyelwa kumsingathi.

hterm_pref_pass_ctrl_tab.message:
Ukuthi u-Ctrl+Tab no-Ctrl+Shift+Tab kuyadluliselwa yini kwisiphequluli.

Uma kuyiqiniso, u-Ctrl+Tab no-Ctrl+Shift+Tab kuzobanjwa isiphequluli njengesinqamuleli sekhibhodi "sethebhu yokulandelayo/okwangaphambilini". Uma kungamanga, ukhiye wethebhu uthunyelwa kumsingathi ngaphandle kuka-Ctrl noma u-Shift.

hterm_pref_pass_ctrl_w.message:
Ukuthi u-Ctrl+W udluliselwe yini kwisiphequluli.

Uma kuyiqiniso, u-Ctrl+W uzosingathwa isiphequluli njengesinqamuleli sekhibhodi "sokuvala ithebhu". Uma kungamanga, u-Ctrl+W uzothunyelwa kumsingathi.

hterm_pref_pass_meta_number.message:
Ukuthi i-Meta+1..9 idluliselwe yini kwisiphequluli.

Lokhu kuwusizo lapho usebenzisa i-hterm kuthebhu yesiphequluli, ukuze ungalahlekelwa izinqamuleli zekhibhodi ze-Chrome zokuthi "shintshela kwithebhu". Lapho kungasebenzi kuthebhu kungcono ukuthumela labo khiye kumsingathi ukuze basetshenziswe ku-vim noma ku-emacs.

Uma kuyiqiniso, i-Meta+1..9 izophathwa isiphequluli. Uma kungamanga, i-Meta+1..9 izothunyelwa kumsingathi. Uma kuyize, thola ngokuzenzekelayo ngokususelwe kwinkundla yesiphequluli nohlobo lewindi.

hterm_pref_pass_meta_v.message:
Ukuthi u-Meta+V uyadluliselwa yini isiphequluli.

Kwamanye amasistimu, lokhu kusetshenziselwa ukunamathisela okuqukethwe.

hterm_pref_paste_on_drop.message:
Uma kuyiqiniso, Umbhalo ohuduliwe wadedelwa uzonamathisela kwitheminali.
Uma kungamanga, umbhalo odedeliwe uzozitshwa.

hterm_pref_receive_encoding.message:
Setha umbhalo wekhodi olindelekile wedatha etholakele kusuka kumsingathi.
Uma umbhalo wekhodi ungafani, iziphazamisi ezibukwayo zingase zingabonwa.

Amanani avumelekile ngu-utf-8' no-'raw'.

hterm_pref_screen_padding_size.message:
Usayizi wogqinsi kuma-pixel ozungeze umngcele wesikrini setheminali.

Lokhu kulawula usayizi womngcele ozungeze isikrini setheminali ukuze umsebenzisi akwazi ukwengeza ugqinsi olubonakalayo onqenqemeni lwesikrini.

hterm_pref_scroll_on_keystroke.message: Ukuthi uskrole yini ngezansi kunoma yikuphi ukuthinta ukhiye.

hterm_pref_scroll_on_output.message: Ukuthi uskrole yini ngezansi kokukhiphayo kwetheminali.

hterm_pref_scroll_wheel_may_send_arrow_k.message:
Lapho usebenzisa enye ibhafa yesikrini, futhi i-DECCKM (Application Cursor Keys) isebenza, imicimbi yesondo lokuskrola ngegundane lizolingisa okhiye bomcibisholo.

Ingakhutshazwa okwesikhashana, ngokubamba ukhiye othi Shift.

Lokhu kuvela njalo lapho usebenzisa amapheyija (less) noma ufunda amakhasi ayinhloko noma abahleli bombhalo (vi/nano) noma usebenzisa isikrini/tmux.

hterm_pref_scroll_wheel_move_multiplier.message:
Isiphindi semicimbi yesondo lokuskrola igundane lapho sikalwe ngama-pixel.

Kushintsha indlela ikhasi elishesha ukuskrola ngayo.

hterm_pref_shift_insert_paste.message: Ukuthi u-Shift+Insert uyasetshenziswa yini ukunamathisela noma ukuthumela kumsingathi okude.

hterm_pref_terminal_encoding.message:
Umbhalo wekhodi wetheminali ezenzakalelayo (DOCS).

I-ISO-2022 inika amandla ukuhunyushwa kwemephu yohlamvu (njengamamephu wemifanekiso).
I-UTF-8 ukusekelwa kwalezo.

Umehluko ovaliwe usho ukuthi umbhalo wekhodi awukwazi ukushintshwa ngesikhathi sokusebenza ngokulandelana kokuphuma ngetheminali.

Kufanele uncike ku-UTF-8 ngaphandle uma uqaphela ukunikezela okunqamukile ngezinhlelo zokusebenza zefa.

hterm_pref_use_default_window_copy.message:
Ukuthi usebenzise yini ukukopisha ukuziphatha kwesiphequluli esisenzakalelayo/OS.

Vumela isiphequluli/OS ukubamba umcimbi wokukopisha ngokuqondile okungase kuthuthukise ukuhambelana namanye amasistimu (lapho ukukopisha kungasebenzi nhlobo), kodwa kwenza ukukhetha umbhalo kungabi namandla kakhulu.

Ngokwesibonelo, imigqa emide ngaphambilini eyayigoqwe emgqeni izokopishwa kanye nemigqa emisha isekhona kuyo.

hterm_pref_word_break_match_left.message:
Izengezo ezivamile zokuyeka okufanayo ngakwesokunxele (ukuqala) kokukhethiwe.

Ngokuvamile lesi isigaba sohlamvu sokwenqaba izinhlamvu ezithile.
Sivumela okuthi "~" nokuthi "." ngokuzenzekelayo ngoba ngokuvamile izindlela ziqala ngalokho

hterm_pref_word_break_match_middle.message:
Izengezo ezivamile zokufanisa zonke izinhlamvu eziphakathi nendawo.

Ngokuvamile lesi isigaba sohlamvu sokwenqaba izinhlamvu ezithile.

Kusetshenziselwa ukunweba okukhethiwe okuzungeze iphoyinti lokuqalisa.

hterm_pref_word_break_match_right.message:
Izengezo ezivamile zokuyeka okufanayo ngakwesokudla (ukuphela) kokukhethiwe.

Ngokuvamile lesi isigaba sohlamvu sokwenqaba izinhlamvu ezithile.

migrate_to_ext.message:
Isaziso: Sicela uthuthele kwisandiso esisha se-Secure Shell ($1).
Izinhlelo Zokusebenza Ze-Chrome zihoxisiwe, ngakho le nguqulo izoyeka ukuthola izibuyekezo.
Sicela ubone umhlahlandlela wokuthuthela ku-($2) ukuthola imininingwane eyengeziwe.

nasftp_cmd_clip_help.message: Kopisha ifayela ebhodini lokunamathisela (okuzenzakalelayo: ngu-10MiB kusuka ekuqaleni)

nasftp_error_internal.message: Iphutha langaphakathi elingasingathiwe, sicela ubike isiphazamisi: $1

omnibox_default.message: <url><match>user@hostname[:port]</match></url> Xhuma kwiphrofayela elondoloziwe noma kwisistimu entsha ye-ssh

open_as_window_tip.message:
[Ithiphu] Sebenzisa okuthi 'Vula njengewindi' noma 'Isikrini esigcwele' ukugwema i-Ctrl+W ekuvaleni itheminali yakho!
[Ithiphu] Bona i-$1 ukuthola ulwazi olwengeziwe.

protocol_register_explain.message: Inkinobho engezansi izozama ukubhalisa izibambi zawo wonke amaphrothokholi esiwasekelayo. Ngokwesibonelo, lokhu kusivumela ukuthi siphathe izixhumanisi ze-ssh:// ngokuqondile. Isexwayiso sizoboniswa isiphequluli sephrothokholi ngayinye, ngakho sicela uqinisekise/wamukele ngayinye njengoba kubonisiwe. Uma zingekho izexwayiso ezibonisiwe, sicela ubone isigaba esilandelayo ukuthola amathiphu wokuxazulula inkinga.

protocol_register_explain_settings.message: Uma sesibhalise kakade izibambi, noma uma imizamo yokubhalisa yangaphambilini iye yanqatshelwa, azikho izexwayiso ezengeziwe ezizoboniswa. Sicela uvule ibhokisi ngezansi, bese uhlola amasethingi wesibambi esibhalisiwe ezigabeni zokuthi ssh/sftp/etc... . Uma lolu hlelo luvinjelwe, ungasusa lawo masethingi azokuvumela ukuthi uzame kabusha ukubhalisa. Uma lolu hlelo lubhalisiwe kakade, kodwa lungasethiwe njengesibambi esizenzakalelayo, ungashintsha futhi nesibambi esizenzakalelayo.
